Krynn Adventurer Guilds
=======================

Last modified by:
Teth, Feb 19, 1997

This document is intended to outline the location of and skills
offered by Adventurer Guilds in the Krynn domain. It is important
to keep in mind, whatever the case, the Adventurer Guilds can not
train more than a sum of 400 levels of skills, and those skills
offered must conform to the details as outlined by 'man skills'.

Solace 'House of Adventurers'
    - /d/Krynn/solace/new_village/adv_guild.c
    - Trainer : Sasha (/d/Krynn/solace/new_village/npc/sasha.c)

Skills offered:
---------------
Animal Handling      30
Appraise Monster     30
Appraise Object      30
Climb                45
Club                 20
Defence              20
Location Sense       30
Open Lock            20
Polearm              15
Sneak                15
Swim                 45
Sword                30
-----------------------
                    330 out of a possible 400 allowable.

Vingaard Keep Adventurer's Guild
    - /d/Krynn/solamn/vin/room/adv_guild.c
    - Talia (/d/Krynn/solamn/vin/npc/talia.c)

Skills offered:
---------------
Animal Handling      30
Appraise Enemy       30
Appraise Object      30
Axe                  30
Blindfighting        20
Knife                30
Sword                30
Tracking             30
Unarmed Combat       20
-----------------------
                    250 out of a possible 400 allowable.


